Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰總部來電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自00：30起放棄B防線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退至最終防線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為第四小隊調撥救援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全軍開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須死守最終防線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則將殃及軌道升降機的技術人員與家屬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護他們是我們作為軍人的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但赫利也在第四小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早有覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親的遺體並沒有被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自那之後 很少和父親說話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親嚴守軍紀 卻害死母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光學探測器在低軌道環上捕捉到大型物體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然造了兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真打算發射嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事能被允許嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用衛星武器攻擊低軌道空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想必不會介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令為實現恆久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早做好了背負所有罪責的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類必須銘記死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思考和平的來之不易
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知全體工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加緊市民往地面的疏散工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記向地面部隊報告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員準備撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把市民脅為人質那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦就下定決心把知道真相的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也作為反聯邦勢力對待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦不惜摧毀這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪走六萬條人命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞏固其統治地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,產業革命以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類獲得了機械文明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑借其智慧面對滅亡的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偉大的領導者們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數十年後壽終正寢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世間再次回到渾沌時代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是世界的…人類的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類未從歷史中吸取教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以伊歐利亞．舒恩伯格創造了變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人上人以其超出常人的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救人類於滅亡的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為即將到來的對話做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們能夠完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎忘記是我造了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言 我是創造之主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領人類的並非變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是我 利馮茲．阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電力供給38%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統工作正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充能完成同時開始掃射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耗費一個多世紀建造而成的人類智慧結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰飛煙滅的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS那群傢伙露出本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是變革者在幕後指使的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆部隊正在紛紛撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們事到如今還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太鹵莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是預測衛星武器對低軌道站的破壞情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓托勒密上宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧 這種狀態下不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事關數萬人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這身體別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠阻止衛星武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有00-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰計畫就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser上需要機師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是拜託拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你駕駛0-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關六萬條人命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為保護而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功概率也許很低
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不想在開始前就放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為保護而戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上它去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 保護生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用彈射器進行二次加速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是機械 不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 第1第3閘門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈射時機轉讓給兩機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈．庫斯洛德 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,台體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 合體模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市民與軍士全部轉移至地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也撤離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本次作戰指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要留到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把即將發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把真相傳給後世…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想靠這種事償還罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍人要保護市民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能多的拯救市民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後才能死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊狀態 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電力供給93%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動Empruss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓縮粒子完全釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動Raiser系統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為布林報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電力供給完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始掃射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始掃射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高能量體接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏離了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是炮擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是光束軍刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別…別
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別阿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低軌道站的下層塔身開始自動解體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查自動平衡器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認錨釘釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔身的外壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷射命中塔身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔身外壁被自動解體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平流層上方的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在絕熱壓縮下被空氣加熱燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下方的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會墜落地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只需要考慮如何減少損失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軌道升降機…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在倒塌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知當前空域所有機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？\N使用有視界通信傳送數據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請摧毀資料所指區城內的塔身碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是人口密集區城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會有數千萬人喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託 救救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓縮粒子 釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Bit展開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Bit展開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為保護生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政變派的機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算避免直接擊中城市圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下所有人團結一致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真夠諷刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷有MS部隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞅準這時候來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓艾迪他們撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果指揮官是她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會拋棄生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要選擇不同於父親的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機體從塔裡出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是叛亂分子主犯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝協助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是史米盧佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是比利斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在MS裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是哈庫裡上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 大型碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 沒有自動解體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN火箭炮 超級轟擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 阿勒路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軌道升降機…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後世界會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲也無法傳到…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘絕人寰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 哈庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種慘劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種無法挽回的慘劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這慘劇是你們引發的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道投靠了叛亂分子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為嚴守軍紀害死了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現今卻投身政變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍人的楷模如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史米盧佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有不測
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時不知該如何面對封閉了心靈的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺少努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史米盧佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軌道升降機倒塌後4個月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風雲變幻的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們只能隨波逐流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 交錯的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭中有誰在呼喊
